data.description: If you are looking for a spacious home that is completely move in ready, this is a must see! Beautifully remodeled tri-level home with over 2300 sq ft. 4 bedrooms plus a study/office or it could serve as a 5th bedroom, 2.5 baths. The main level has attractive and durable luxury vinyl throughout. The kitchen has been gorgeously updated with 42 inch cabinets, a large penisula to add storage and seating, laminate counters, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash and lighting. The family room is open to the kitchen and dining area, with new sliding patio doors leading to the huge rear deck. The laundry is conveniently located with the half bath and is on the main level.  2 Full bathrooms are located on the upper level and both are remodeled top to bottom. The owner's suite offers a walk in closet, large bathroom featuring a double vanity, tile, tub/shower, lighting, mirrors and storage. The main hall bath is as equally stylishly remodeled. The walk out lower level offers a rec room/home gym/media room (use it how it best suits you) with new flooring and is freshly painted, plus there is a generous storage area. In the back yard there is a new storage shed and yard is fenced. There is an extra parking area on the side of home behind the gate. Radon mitigation system installed 2020. Roof 2015, Furnace 2014, AC 2009. The oversized 1 car garage provides storage space in addition to the parking area. This is a wonderful home with so much space. You really have to see it in person!
